quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  10,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  10,1,"a l- ray, yeh uss kitaab ki ayaat hain jo hikmat o Danish se labraiz hai"
  10,2,kya logon ke liye yeh aik ajeeb baat ho gayi ke hum ne khud aُnhi mein se aik aadmi ko ishara kya ke ( ghaflat mein parre hue ) logon ko chonka day aur jo maan len un ko khushkhabri dide ke un ke liye unn ke rab ke paas sachhi izzat o sarfarazi hai? ( kya yahi woh baat hai jis par ) munkareen ne kaha ke yeh shakhs to khula jadugar hai ?
  10,3,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhara rab wohi khuda hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay dinon mein peda kya, phir takhat hukoomat par jalva gir howa aur kaayenaat ka intizam chala raha hai koi Shafaat ( sifarish ) karne wala nahi ila yeh ke is ki ijazat ke baad Shafaat kere yahi Allah tumhara rab hai lehaza tum usi ki ibadat karo phir kya tum hosh mein nah aao ge ?"
  10,4,"isi ki taraf tum sab ko palat kar jana hai, yeh Allah ka pakka wada hai be shak paidaiesh ki ibtida wohi karta hai, phir wohi dobarah peda kere ga, taakay jo log imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye un ko poooray insaaf ke sath jaza day, aur jinhon ne kufar ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kya woh kholta howa pani پییں aur dard naak saza bhgtin uss inkaar haq ki Padaash mein jo woh karte rahay"
  10,5,wohi hai jis ne sooraj ko Ujyala banaya aur chaand ko chamak di aur chaand ke ghatney bherne ki manzilain theek theek muqarrar kar den taakay tum uss se barson aur tarikhon ke hisaab maloom karo Allah ne yeh sab kuch ( khail ke tor par nahi balkay ) ba maqsad hi banaya hai woh apni nshanyon ko khol khol kar paish kar raha hai unn logon ke liye jo ilm rakhtay hain
  10,6,"yaqeenan raat aur din ke ulat phair mein aur har uss cheez mein jo Allah ne zameen aur asmano mein peda ki hai, nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ( ghalat beeni o ghalat rawi se ) bachna chahtay hain"
  10,7,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log hum se milnay ki tawaqqa nahi rakhtay aur duniya ki zindagi hi par raazi aur mutmaen ho gay hain, aur jo log hamari nshanyon se ghaafil hain"
  10,8,unn ka aakhri thikana jahannum ho ga unn buraiyon ki Padaash mein jin ka Iktisab woh ( apne is ghalat aqeday aur ghalat tarz amal ki wajah se ) karte rahay
  10,9,"aur yeh bhi haqeeqat hai ke jo log imaan laaye ( yani jinhon ne unn sadaqaton ko qubool kar liya jo is kitaab mein paish ki gayi hain ) aur naik aamaal karte rahay inhen unn ka rab unn ke imaan ki wajah se seedhi raah chalaye ga, Nemat bharijannaton mein un ke neechay nhrin behain gi"
  10,10,"wahan un ki sada yeh hogi ke “pak hai to ae khuda,"" unn ki dua yeh hogi ke “slamtiho"" aur un ki har baat ka khtama is par hoga ke “sari tareef Allah rab alaalmin hi ke liye hai """
  10,11,agar kahin Allah logon ke sath bura maamla karne mein bhi itni hi jaldi karta jitni woh duniya ki bhalai mangnay mein jaldi karte hain to un ki mohlat amal kabhi ki khatam kar di gayi hoti ( magar hamara yeh tareeqa nahi hai ) is liye hum unn logon ko jo hum se milnay ki tawaqqa nahi rakhtay unn ki sar kashi mein bhatakne ke liye chhُot day dete hain
  10,12,"ensaan ka haal yeh hai ke jab is par koi sakht waqt aata hai to kharray aur baithy aur letey hum ko pukaarta hai, magar jab hum is ki museebat taall dete hain to aisa chal nikalta hai ke goya is ne kabhi apne kisi buray waqt par hum ko puraka hi nah tha is terhan hadd se guzar jaane walon ke liye un ke kartoot khushnuma bana diye gay hain"
  10,13,"logo, tum se pehlay ki qomon ko ( jo apne apne zamana mein brsr urooj theen ) hum ne halaak kar diya jab unhon ne zulm ki rawish ikhtiyar ki aur unn ke rasool unn ke paas khُli khُli nishanain le kar aeye aur unhon ne imaan laa kar hi nah diya is terhan hum mujrimon ko un ke juraim ka badla diya karte hain"
  10,14,ab un ke baad hum ne tum ko zameen mein un ki jagah di hai taakay dekhen tum kaisay amal karte ho
  10,15,"jab inhen hamari saaf saaf baatein sُnayi jati hain to woh log jo hum se milnay ki tawaqqa nahi rakhtay, kehte hain ke “as ke bajaye koi aur quran lao ya is mein kuch tarmeem karo"" ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho “میرا yeh kaam nahi hai ke apni taraf se is mein koi tagayur o tabdal kar lon mein to bas uss wahi ka pairo hon jo mere paas bhaije jati hai agar mein apne rab ki nafarmani karoon to mujhe aik barray holnaak din ke azaab ka dar hai """
  10,16,"aur kaho “agar Allah ki mushiyat nah hoti to mein yeh quran tumhe kabhi nah sunataa aur Allah tumhe is ki khabar taq nah deta aakhir is se pehlay mein aik Umar tumahray darmain guzaar chuka hon, kya tum aqal se kaam nahi letay ?"
  10,17,"phir uss se barh kar zalim aur kon ho ga jo aik jhooti baat ghurr kar Allah ki taraf mansoob kere ya Allah ki waqai ayaat ko jhoota qarar day yaqeenan mujrim kabhi Falah nahi pa satke """
  10,18,"yeh log Allah ke siwa unn ki parastish kar rahay hain jo un ko nah nuqsaan pouncha satke hain nah naffa, aur kehte yeh hain ke yeh Allah ke haan hamaray safarishi hain ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho “کیا tum Allah ko uss baat ki khabar dete ho jisay woh nah asmano mein jaanta hai nah zameen mein ?"" pak hai woh aur baala o bartar hai uss shirk se jo yeh log karte hain"
  10,19,"ibtida saaray ensaan aik hi ammt thay, baad mein unhon ne mukhtalif aqeday aur maslak bana liye, aur agar tairay rab ki taraf se pehlay hi aik baat tey nah kar li gayi hoti to jis cheez mein woh baahum ikhtilaaf kar rahay hain is ka faisla kar diya jata"
  10,20,"aur yeh jo woh kehte hain ke iss NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam par is ke rab ki taraf se koi nishani kyun nah utari gayi, to un se kaho “ghaib ka maalik o mukhtaar to Allah hi hai, acha, intzaar karo, mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon """
  10,21,"logon ka haal yeh hai ke museebat ke baad jab hum un ko rehmat ka maza chakkhatay hain to foran hi woh hamari nshanyon ke maamla mein chaal bazyan shuru kar dete hain un se kaho “Allah apni chaal mein tum se ziyada taiz hai, is ke farishtay tumhari sab mkaryoN ko qalam band kar rahay hain """
  10,22,"woh Allah hi hai jo tum ko khushki aur tri mein chalata hai chunancha jab tum kashtiyon mein sawaar ho kar baad-e mawafiq par Ferhan o Shadan safar kar rahay hotay ho aur phir yakayak baad-e mukhalif ka zor hota hai aur har taraf se moajoon ke thpirhe lagtay hain aur musafir samajh letay hain ke tufaan mein ghar gay, uss waqt sab apne deen ko Allah hi ke liye khalis kar ke is se Duayen mangte hain ke “ agar to ne hum ko is bulaa se nijaat day di to hum shukar guzaar bande banin ge """
  10,23,"magar jab woh un ko bacha laita hai to phir wohi log haq se munharif ho kar zameen mein baghaawat karne lagtay hain logo, tumhari yeh baghaawat Ulti tumahray hi khilaaf par rahi hai duniya ke chand roza mazay hain ( lُot lau ), phir hamari taraf tumhe palat kar aana hai, uss waqt hum tumhe bta den ge ke tum kya kuch karte rahay ho"
  10,24,"duniya ki yeh zindagi ( jis ke nashay mein mast ho kar tum hamari nshanyon se ghaflat bart rahay ho ) is ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aasman se hum ne pani barsaya to zameen ki pedawar, jisay aadmi aur janwar sab khatay hain, khoob ghani ho gayi, phir ain uss waqt jabkay zameen apni bahhar par thi aur khityan bani snori khari theen aur un ke maalik yeh samajh rahay thay ke ab hum un se faida aُthane par Qadir hain, yakayak raat ko ya din ko hamara hukum aa gaya aur hum ne usay aisa ghaarat kar ke rakh diya ke goya kal wahan kuch tha hi nahi is terhan hum nishanain khol khol kar paish karte hain unn logon ke liye jo sochnay samajhney walay hain"
  10,25,( tum iss na paidaar zindagi ke fraib mein mubtala ho rahay ho ) aur Allah tumhe daar salam ki taraf dawat day raha hai ( hadaayat uss ke ikhtiyar mein hai ) jis ko woh chahta hai seedha rasta dikha deta hai
  10,26,jin logon ne BHALAI ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kya un ke liye BHALAI hai aur mazeed fazl un ke cheharon par roo siyahi aur zillat nah chaaye gi woh jannat ke mustahiq hain jahan woh hamesha rahen ge
  10,27,"aur jin logon ne buraiyan kamaain un ki buraii jaisi hai waisa hi woh badla payen ge, zillat un par musallat ho gi, koi Allah se un ko bachanay wala nah ho ga, un ke cheharon par aisi tareqi chhai hui ho gi jaisay raat ke siyah parday un par parre hue hon, woh dozakh ke mustahiq hain jahan woh hamesha rahen ge"
  10,28,"jis roz hum un sab ko aik sath ( apni adalat mein ) akhatta karen ge, phir un logon se jinhon ne shirk kya hai kahein ge ke tehrjao tum bhi aur tumahray banaye hue shareek bhi, phir hum un ke darmain se ajnabaiyat ka parda hata den ge aur un ke shareek kahin ge ke “ tum hamari ibadat to nahi karte thay"
  10,29,"hamaray aur tumahray darmain Allah ki gawahi kaafi hai ke ( tum agar hamari ibadat karte bhi thay to ) hum tumhari is ibadat se bilkul be khabar thay """
  10,30,"uss waqt har shakhs apne kiye ka maza chakh le ga, sab apne maalik haqeeqi ki taraf phair diye jayen ge aur woh saaray jhoot jo unhon ne ghurr rakhay thay gum ho jayen ge"
  10,31,"inn se pucho, kon tum ko aasman aur zameen se rizaq deta hai? yeh samaat aur benaye ki quwaten kis ke ikhtiyar mein hain? kon be jaan mein se jandaar ko aur jandaar mein se be jaan ko nkalta hai? kon iss nazam aalam ki tadbeer kar raha hai? woh zaroor kahin ge ke Allah kaho, phir tum ( haqeeqat ke khilaaf chalne se ) parhaiz nahi karte ?"
  10,32,tab to yahi Allah tumhara haqeeqi rab hai phir haq ke baad gumraahi ke siwa aur kya baqi reh gaya? aakhir yeh tum kidhar phira-ay ja rahay ho ?
  10,33,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, dekho ) is terhan nafarmani ikhtiyar karne walon par tumahray rab ki baat Sadiq aa gayi ke woh maan kar nah den ge"
  10,34,"inn se pucho, tumahray tehra-ay hue sharikon mein koi hai jo takhleeq ki ibtida bhi karta ho aur phir is ka iada bhi kere? kaho woh sirf Allah hai jo takhleeq ki ibtida bhi karta hai aur is ka iada bhi, phir tum yeh kis Ulti raah par chalaye ja rahay ho ?"
  10,35,"inn se pucho tumahray tehra-ay hue sharikon mein koi aisa bhi hai jo haq ki taraf rahnumai karta ho? kaho woh sirf Allah hai jo haq ki taraf rahnumai karta hai phir bhala batao, jo haq ki taraf rahnumai karta hai woh iss ka ziyada mustahiq hai ke is ki pairwi ki jaye ya woh jo khud raah nahi paata ila yeh ke is ki rahnumai ki jaye? aakhir tumhe ho kya gaya hai, kaisay ultay ultay faislay karte ho ?"
  10,36,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke inn mein se aksar log mehez qiyaas o gumaan ke peechay chalay ja rahay hain, halan ke gumaan haq ki zaroorat ko kuch bhi poora nahi karta jo kuch yeh kar rahay hain Allah uss ko khoob jaanta hai"
  10,37,aur yeh quran woh cheez nahi hai jo Allah ki wahi o taleem ke baghair tasneef kar liya jaye balkay yeh to jo kuch pehlay aa chuka tha is ki tasdeeq aur al-kitab ki tafseel hai iss mein koi shak nahi ke yeh frmanrwaye kaayenaat ki taraf se hai
  10,38,"kya yeh log kehte hain kePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamne usay khud tasneef kar liya hai? kaho, “ agar tum apne is ilzaam mein sachey ho to aik soorah is jaisi tasneef kar lao aur aik khuda ko chore kar jis jis ko bُla satke ho madad ke liye bُla lau """
  10,39,"asal yeh hai ke jo cheez inn ke ilm ki girift mein nahi aayi aur jis ka مآل bhi un ke samnay nahi aaya, uss ko unhon ne ( khamkhuwa atkal pacho ) jhutla diya isi terhan to un se pehlay ke log bhi jhutla chuke hain phir dekh lau unn zaalmon ka kya injaam howa"
  10,40,inn mein se kuch log imaan layein ge aur kuch nahi layein ge aur tera rab unn mfsdon ko khoob jaanta hai
  10,41,"agar yeh tujhe jutlatay hain to keh day ke “mera amal mere liye hai aur tumhara amal tumahray liye, jo kuch mein karta hon is ki zimma daari se tum bari ho aur jo kuch tum kar rahay ho is ki zimma daari se mein bari hon """
  10,42,"un mein bohat se log hain jo teri baatein suntay hain, magar kya to behroon ko sunayega khuwa woh kuch nah samajte hon ?"
  10,43,"inn mein bohat se log hain jo tujhe dekhte hain, magar kya to andhon ko raah betaye ga khuwa inhen kuch nah sujhta ho ?"
  10,44,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah logon par zulm nahi karta, log khud hi apne ooper zulm karte hain"
  10,45,( aaj yeh duniya ki zindagi mein mast hain ) aur jis roz Allah inn ko akhatta kere ga to ( yahi duniya ki zindagi aِnhin aisi mahsoos hogi ) goya yeh mehez aik gharri bhar aapas mein jaan pehchan karne ko thire thay ( is waqt tahaqeeq ho jaye ga ke ) fi al waqea sakht ghatay mein rahay woh log jinhon ne Allah ki mulaqaat ko jhtlaya aur hargiz woh raah e raast par nah thay
  10,46,"jin buray nataij se hum inhen dara rahay hain un ka koi hissa hum tairay jeetay jee dikha den ya is se pehlay hi tujhe uttha len, behar haal aِnhin aana hamari hi taraf hai aur jo kuch yeh kar rahay hain is par Allah gawah hai"
  10,47,har ammt ke liye aik rasool hai phir jab kisi ammt ke paas uss ka rasool aa jata hai to is ka faisla poooray insaaf ke sath chuka diya jata hai aur is par zarra barabar zulm nahi kya jata
  10,48,kehte hain agar tumhari yeh dhamki sachhi hai to aakhir yeh kab poori ho gi ?
  10,49,"kaho “mereikhtiyar mein khud apna naffa o zarrar bhi nahi, sab kuch Allah ki mushiyat par moqoof hai har ammt ke liye mohlat ki aik mddt hai, jab yeh mddt poori ho jati hai to gharri bhar ki taqdeem o takheer bhi nahi hoti """
  10,50,"inn se kaho, kabhi tum ne yeh bhi socha ke agar Allah ka azaab achanak raat ko ya din ko aa jaye ( to tum kya kar satke ho? ) aakhir yeh aisi konsi cheez hai jis ke liye mujrim jaldi machayen ?"
  10,51,kya jab woh tum par aa parre isi waqt tum usay manu ge? ab bachna chahtay ho? halaank tum khud hi is ke jaldi anay ka taqaza kar rahay thay !
  10,52,"phir zaalmon se kaha jaye ga ke ab hamesha ke azaab ka maza chako, jo kuch tum kamate rahay ho is ki Padaash ke siwa aur kya badla tum ko diya ja sakta hai ?"
  10,53,"phir poochtay hain kya waqai yeh sach hai jo tum keh rahay ho? kaho “mere Rab ki qasam, yeh bilkul sach hai aur tum itna bil bota nahi rakhtay ke usay zahoor mein anay se rok do """
  10,54,"agar har uss shakhs ke paas jis ne zulm kya hai, Roye zameen ki doulat bhi ho to uss azaab se bachney ke liye woh usay Fidya mein dainay par amaada ho jaye ga jab yeh log is azaab ko dekh len ge to dil hi dil mein puchta-ayn ge magar un ke darmain poooray insaaf se faisla kya jaye ga koi zulm un par nah ho ga"
  10,55,suno! asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai Allah ka hai sun rakho! Allah ka wada schcha hai magar aksar ensaan jantay nahi hain
  10,56,wohi zindagi bkhshta hai aur wohi mout deta hai aur isi ki taraf tum sab ko palatna hai
  10,57,logo! tumahray paas tumahray rab ki taraf se nasiyaat aa gayi hai yeh woh cheez hai jo dilon ke amraaz ki Shifa hai aur jo usay qubool kar len un ke liye rahnumai aur rehmat hai
  10,58,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kaho ke “ih Allah ka fazl aur is ki meharbani hai ke yeh cheez is ne bhaije, is par to logon ko khusi mnanai chahiye, yeh unn sab cheezon se behtar hai jinhein log samaitt rahay hain """
  10,59,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho “تم logon ne kabhi yeh bhi socha hai ke jo rizaq Allah ne tumahray liye utaara tha is mein se tum ne khud hi kisi ko haraam aur kisi ko halaltehra liya !"" inn se pucho, Allah ne tum ko is ki ijazat di thi? ya tum Allah par aftara kar rahay ho ?"
  10,60,jo log Allah par yeh jhoota aftara bandhte hain un ka kya gumaan hai ke qayamat ke roz un se kya maamla ho ga? Allah to logon par meharbani ki nazar rakhta hai magar aksar ensaan aisay hain jo shukar nahi karte
  10,61,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum jis haal mein bhi hotay ho aur quran mein se jo kuch bhi sanatay ho, aur logo, tum bhi jo kuch karte ho uss sab ke douran mein hum tum ko dekhte rehtay hain koi zarra barabar cheez aasman aur zameen mein aisi nahi hai, nah choti nah barri, jo tairay rab ki nazar se posheeda ho aur aik saaf daftar mein darj nah ho"
  10,62,"sunooooooo! jo Allah ke dost hain, jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne taqwa ka rawayya ikhtiyar kya ,"
  10,63,un ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi hai
  10,64,duniya aur akhirat dono zindagion mein un ke liye basharat hi basharat hai Allah ki baatein badal nahi sakteen yahi barri kamyabi hai
  10,65,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jo baatein yeh log tujh par banatay hain woh tujhe ranjida nah karen, azzt saari ki saari khuda ke ikhtiyar mein hai, aur woh sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
  10,66,"aagah raho! aasman ke basnay walay hon ya zameen ke, sab se sab Allah ke mamlook hain aur jo log Allah ke siwa kuch ( apne khodsakht_h ) sharikon ko pukaar rahay hain woh niray wahm- o- gumaan ke pairo hain aur mehez qiyaas aarayyan karte hain"
  10,67,woh Allah hi hai jis ne tumahray liye raat banai ke is mein sukoon haasil karo aur din ko roshan banaya is mein nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ( khulay kaanon se paighambar ki dawat ko ) suntay hain
  10,68,"logon ne keh diya ke Allah ne kisi ko beta banaya hai subhan Allah ! woh to be niaz hai, asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai sab is ki malik hai tumahray paas is qoul ke liye aakhir kya Daleel hai? kya tum Allah ke mutaliq woh baatein kehte ho jo tumahray ilm mein nahi hain ?"
  10,69,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, keh do ke jo log Allah par jhutay aftara bandhte hain woh hargiz Falah nahi pa satke"
  10,70,"duniya ki chand roza zindagi mein mazay kar len, phir hamari taraf unn ko palatna hai phir hum is kufar ke badlay jis ka irtikaab woh kar rahay hain un ko sakht azaab ka maza chkhayin ge"
  10,71,"inn ko Nooh ka qissa sunaaoo, uss waqt ka qissa jab uss ne apni qoum se kaha tha ke “اے baradran qoum, agar mera tumahray darmain rehna aur Allah ki ayaat suna suna kar tumhe ghaflat se beedar karna tumahray liye na qabil bardasht ho gaya hai to mera bharosa Allah par hai, tum apne tehra-ay hue sharikon ko sath le kar aik mutafiqa faisla kar lau aur jo mansoobah tumahray paish e nazar ho is ko khoob soch samajh lau taakay is ka ko yi pehlu tumhari nigah se posheeda nah rahay, phir mere khilaaf is ko amal mein le aao aur mujhe hargiz mohlat nah do"
  10,72,"tum ne meri nasiyaat se mun morra ( to mera kya nuqsaan kya ) mein tum se kisi ajar ka talab gaar nah tha, mera ajar to Allah ke zimma hai aur mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke ( khuwa koi manay ya nah manay ) mein khud muslim ban kar rahon """
  10,73,"unhon ne usay jhtlaya aur nateeja yeh howa ke hum ne usay aur unn logon ko jo is ke sath kashti mein thay, bacha liya aur unhi ko zameen mein janasheen banaya aur un sab logon ko ghark kar diya jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko jhtlaya tha pas dekh lau ke jinhein mutnabba kya gaya tha ( aur phir bhi unhon ne maan kar nah diya ) unn ka kya injaam howa"
  10,74,"phir Nooh ke baad hum ne mukhtalif payghambaroon ko unn ki qomon ki taraf bheja aur woh unn ke paas khuli khuli nishanain le kar aeye, magar jis cheez ko unhon ne pehlay jhutla diya tha usay phir maan kar nah diya is terhan hum hadd se guzar jaane walon ke dilon par thp_h laga dete hain"
  10,75,"phir un ke baad hum ne moose aur haroon ko apni nshanyon ke sath firaon aur is ke sardaro ki taraf bheja, magar unhon ne apni barayi ka ghamand kya aur woh mujrim log thay"
  10,76,pas jab hamaray paas se haq un ke samnay aaya to unhon ne keh diya ke yeh to khula jaadoo hai
  10,77,"moose ne kaha : “تم haq ko yeh kehte ho jabkay woh tumahray samnay agaya? kya yeh jaadoo hai? halaank jaadoo gir Falah nahi paaya karte """
  10,78,"onhon ne jawab mein kaha “کیا twas liye aaya hai ke hamein aُ seen tareeqay se phair day jis par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya hai aur zameen mein barayi tum dono ki qaim ho jaye? tumahray baat to hum maan-ne walay nahi hain """
  10,79,"aur firaon ne ( apne admion se ) kaha ke “har maahir fun jadugar ko mere paas haazir karo """
  10,80,"jab jaadoo gir aa gay to moose ne un se kaha “jo kuch tumhe phenkna hai phenko """
  10,81,"phir jab unhon ne apne آAnnchar pheink diye to moose ne kaha “ih jo kuch tum ne phenka hai yeh jaadoo hai, Allah abhi isay baatil kiye deta hai, mfsdon ke kaam ko Allah sdhrne nahi deta"
  10,82,"aur Allah apne farmanoon se haq ko haq kar dekhata hai, khuwa mujrimon ko woh kitna hi nagawaar ho """
  10,83,"( phir dekho ke ) moose ko is ki qoum mein se chand nojawanon ke siwa kisi ne nah maana, firaon ke dar se aur khud apni qoum ke sir Bar Awerda logon ke dar se ( jinhein khauf tha ke ) firaon un ko azaab mein mubtala kere ga aur waqea yeh hai ke firaon zameen mein ghalba rakhta tha aur woh unn logon mein se tha jo kisi hadd par ruktay nahi hain"
  10,84,"moose ne apni qoum se kaha ke “logo, agar tum waqai Allah par imaan rakhtay ho to is par bharosa karo agar musalman ho """
  10,85,"unhon ne jawab diya “hm ne Allah hi par bharosa kya, ae hamaray rab, hamein zalim logon ke liye fitnah nah bana"
  10,86,"aur apni rehmat se hum ko kafiroon se nijaat day """
  10,87,"aur hum ne moose aur is ke bhai ko ishara kya ke “misar mein chand makaan apni qoum ke liye muhayya karo aur apne un makanon ko qiblatehra lau aur namaz qaim karo aur ahal imaan ko basharat day do """
  10,88,"moose ne dua ki “ayhamaray rab, to ne firaon aur is ke sardaro ko duniya ki zindagi mein zeenat aur amwal se Nawaz rakha hai ae rab, kya yeh is liye hai ke woh logon ko teri raah se buhtka-ayn? ae rab, un ke maal ghaarat kar day aur un ke dilon par aisi mohar kar day ke imaan nah layein jab taq dard naak azaab nah dekh len """
  10,89,"Allah taala ne jawab mein farmaya “تم dono ki dua qubool ki gayi saabit qadam raho aur unn logon ke tareeqay ki hargiz pairwi nah karo jo ilm nahi rakhtay """
  10,90,"aur hum bani Israel ko samandar se guzaar le gay phir firaon aur is ke lashkar zulm aur zayad-ti ki gharz se un ke peechay chalay hatta ke jab firaon doobnay laga to bol utha"" mein ne maan liya ke khudawand haqeeqi uss ke siwa koi nahi hai jis par bani Israel imaan laaye, aur mein bhi sir itaat jhuka dainay walon mein se hon """
  10,91,( jawab diya gaya ) “اab imaan lata hai! halaank iss se pehlay taq to nafarmani karta raha aur fasaad barpaa karne walon mein se tha
  10,92,"ab to hum sirf teri laash hi ko bachayen ge taakay to baad ki naslon ke liye nishaan Ibrat banay agarchay bohat se ensaan aisay hain jo hamari nshanyon se ghaflat brtte hain """
  10,93,hum ne bani Israel ko bohat acha thikana diya aur nihayat umdah wasail zindagi inhen ataa kiye phir unhon ne baahum ikhtilaaf nahi kya mgras waqt jabkay ilm unn ke paas aa chuka tha yaqeenan tera rab qayamat ke roz unn ke darmain uss cheez ka faisla kar day ga jis mein woh ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain
  10,94,"ab agar tujhe uss hadaayat ki taraf se kuch bhi shak ho jo hum ne tujh par nazil ki hai to unn logon se pooch le jo pehlay se kitaab parh rahay hain fi al waqea yeh tairay paas haq hi aaya hai tairay rab ki taraf se, lehaza to shak karne walon mein se nah ho"
  10,95,"aur un logon mein nah shaamil ho jinhon ne Allah ki ayaat ko jhtlaya hai, warna to nuqsaan uthany walon mein se hoga"
  10,96,haqeeqat yeh hai ke jin logon par tairay rab ka qoul raast agaya hai un ke samnay khuwa koi nishani aa jaye
  10,97,woh kabhi imaan laa kar nahi dete jab taq ke dard naak azaab samnay aata nah dekh len
  10,98,phir kya aisi koi misaal hai ke aik bastii azaab dekh kar imaan layi ho aur is ka imaan is ke liye naffa bakhash saabit howa ho? Younis ki qoum ke siwa ( is ki koi nazeer nahi ) woh qoum jab imaan le aayi thi to Albata hum ne is par se duniya ki zindagi mein ruswai ka azaab taall diya tha aur is ko aik muddat taq zindagi se behra mand honay ka mauqa day diya tha
  10,99,agar tairay rab ki Mushiyat yeh hoti ( ke zameen mein sab momin o farmanbardar hi hon ) to saaray ahal zameen imaan le aeye hotay phir kya to logon ko majaboor kere ga ke woh momin ho jayen ?
  10,100,"koi mutnaqas Allah ke azan ke baghair imaan nahi laa sakta, aur Allah ka tareeqa yeh hai ke jo log aqal se kaam nahi letay woh un par gandagi daal deta hai"
  10,101,"inn se kaho “zamin aur asmano mein jo kuch hai usay ankhen khol kar dekho"" aur jo log imaan lana hi nahi chahtay un ke liye nishanain aur tambihain (warnings) aakhir kya mufeed ho sakti hain"
  10,102,"ab yeh log iss ke siwa aur kis cheez ke muntazir hain ke wohi buray din dekhen jo inn se pehlay guzray hue log dekh chuke hain? inn se kaho “achha, intzaar karo, mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon """
  10,103,phir ( jab aisa waqt aata hai to ) hum apne Rasolo-n ko aur unn logon ko bacha liya karte hain jo imaan laaye hon hamara yahi tareeqa hai hum par yeh haq hai ke mominon ko bacha len
  10,104,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! keh do ke logo, agar tum abhi taq mere deen ke mutaliq kisi shak mein ho to sun lau ke tum Allah ke siwa jin ki bandagi karte ho mein un ki bandagi nahi karta balkay sirf isi khuda ki bandagi karta hon jis ke qabzay mein tumhari mout hai mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke mein imaan laane walon mein se hon"
  10,105,"aur mujh se farmaya gaya hai ke to yaksu ho kar apne aap ko theek theek iss deen par qaim kar day, aur hargiz hargiz mushrikon mein se nah ho"
  10,106,aur Allah ko chore kar kisi aisi hasti ko nah pukaar jo tujhe nah faida pouncha sakti hai nah nuqsaan agar to aisa kere ga to zaalmon mein se hoga
  10,107,"agar Allah tujhe kisi museebat mein daaley to khud is ke siwa koi nahi jo is museebat ko taall day, aur agar woh tairay haq mein kisi bhalai ka iradah kere to is ke fazl ko phairnay wala bhi koi nahi hai woh apne bundon mein se jis ko chahta hai apne fazl se nawazta hai aur woh dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  10,108,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, keh do ke “logo, tumahray paas tumahray rab ki taraf se haq aa chuka hai ab jo seedhi raah ikhtiyar kere is ki raast rawi isi ke liye mufeed hai, aur jo gumraah rahay is ki gumraahi isi ke liye tabah kin hai aur mein tumahray oopar koi hawala daar nahi hon """
  10,109,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum is hadaayat ki pairwi kiye jao jo tumhari taraf ba zarea wahi bhaije ja rahi hai, aur sabr karo yahan taq ke Allah faisla kar day, aur wohi behtareen faisla karne wala hai"
